White (silver actually) looks good on the rear bumper. At night it's
impossible to ignore and in the daytime nobody knows it's there:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts8/46-3MOnRearBumper.jpg

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts7/03-LightsOff.jpg

There's no mistaking the red/white combo but I think white on it's own is
effective and doesn't leave your bus looking like it belongs in a
contruction zone.

